# Privacy Policy

This userscript does not collect, store, sell, or share personal data.

The script uses Tornium OAuth only to:
• Identify the logged in Torn user
• Read faction data needed for withdrawal requests
• Submit faction vault withdrawal requests

All OAuth tokens are stored locally in the user's browser via Tampermonkey storage.

No data is transmitted to any external server.

